# ideas/

## What goes here
- Pre-execution concepts that don't yet have a timeline or deliverables
- Hypotheses, brainstorms, or explorations worth remembering

## What does NOT go here
- Active workstreams with deliverables (→ `projects/`)
- Decisions already made (→ `decisions/`)

## Primary Home Test
File here if the concept has no timeline yet.

## Naming Rule
`idea-name.md` (lowercase, hyphenated). Example: `voice-first-crm.md`

## Required Sections
- Executive Summary
- Bias Check
- Current State (maturity, open questions)
- Compiled Truth
- Timeline Evidence
